0x2C033875.name: IS_DISABLED_RAW_KEY_UP

params.name: rawKeyIndex
params.description: Index of raw key from keyboard.

0x2C033875.description:
Gets if the specified `rawKeyIndex` is up, even if the key is disabled with [DISABLE_RAW_KEY_THIS_FRAME](#\_0x8BCF0014).

Virtual key codes can be found [here](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/windows/win32/inputdev/virtual-key-codes)

examples.code:
if IsDisabledRawKeyUp(32) then -- KEY_SPACE
    print("Spacebar is up")
end

0x2C033875.resultsDescription: Returns bool value of up state.
